<h2 class="bold font-l">Accidents Happen</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Grover and Elmo discuss this trope in song, saying that bedwetting is normal for little kids. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
